  "2359600": {
    "name": "Perfect New World",
    "steam_appid": 2359600,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/52a117acec32e1813d8a52a7ea193e66.avif?t=1698896750\" width=616 height=110 /></span><br>Perfect New World is a Boundless World MMO Action RPG, where you shall become a Soul Tamer and search for the reincarnated Prime! Immerse yourself in this fantasy world experience seamlessly as you overcome the dangerous challenges and unveil the mysteries this world has to offer! Team up with friends and explore the secrets scattered across the world, and help its inhabitants solve their various troubles through capturing Spirit Beasts, clearing dangerous dungeons, or conquering monsters in the wilds. Or, if you prefer competing, you can choose to fight other players! Unleash your powerful skills on your opponents and enjoy great combat where every hit packs a punch!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore A Fantasy World With Friends</strong></h2>You and your friends venture into the vast continent of Perfect World in search of mystical powers. Mysteries of all kinds await your discovery. Boosters will unlock new perspectives to help you better explore this unknown world.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/ee7af932c2b79c8bf0c68c9f89647ae4.poster.avif?t=1698896750\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/ee7af932c2b79c8bf0c68c9f89647ae4.webm?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/ee7af932c2b79c8bf0c68c9f89647ae4.mp4?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Select A Race And Customize It Into Anything You Want It To Be</strong></h2>There are four races to choose from: Elvens, Mythics, and Humans. You may choose to be a war-ending Galeblade, a battle-hardened Berserker, an aim-accureated Dragonspear, or a free-spirited Mysticsword. Whoever you choose to be, you can always stand out in a crowd through face customization.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/c89eb199d52f1312debd0b26a04387dc.poster.avif?t=1698896750\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/c89eb199d52f1312debd0b26a04387dc.webm?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/c89eb199d52f1312debd0b26a04387dc.mp4?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Master Class Skills. Build Unique Combos. Experience Hard-Core Combat!</strong></h2>Each class has its unique talent system. Unrestricted skill releases and a wide variety of combos give you a constraint-free combat experience, allowing you to develop your own fighting style.<br><br><br><strong>Dragonspear - New Class of Equilibrious Test</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/49f1a495f439b8db6ebb7024d770f6b6.poster.avif?t=1698896750\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/49f1a495f439b8db6ebb7024d770f6b6.webm?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/49f1a495f439b8db6ebb7024d770f6b6.mp4?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Berserker</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/6ffa18b2fa56f5e4c2e87558b339d6c9.poster.avif?t=1698896750\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/6ffa18b2fa56f5e4c2e87558b339d6c9.webm?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/6ffa18b2fa56f5e4c2e87558b339d6c9.mp4?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Mysticsword</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/34861af639c87600a8aeabcc6d57d1f7.poster.avif?t=1698896750\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/34861af639c87600a8aeabcc6d57d1f7.webm?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/34861af639c87600a8aeabcc6d57d1f7.mp4?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Galeblade</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/053c5c47a749197d33f5577aba5eaefe.poster.avif?t=1698896750\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/053c5c47a749197d33f5577aba5eaefe.webm?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/053c5c47a749197d33f5577aba5eaefe.mp4?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Clear Dungeons And Fight Tough Enemies</strong></h2>You will team up with your friends to brave perilous dungeons and defeat tough enemies, gaining precious materials to power up yourself.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/dd2807743add086793fdee8fad52fc00.poster.avif?t=1698896750\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/dd2807743add086793fdee8fad52fc00.webm?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/dd2807743add086793fdee8fad52fc00.mp4?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Boundless World Rich In Fun Details</strong></h2>Adventures await around every corner. Challenges and encounters abound along the way. Your journey shall be enriched by exciting interactive experiences.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/e0fac0544cecf6ffcdbdb5c97d6ca967.poster.avif?t=1698896750\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/e0fac0544cecf6ffcdbdb5c97d6ca967.webm?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359600/extras/e0fac0544cecf6ffcdbdb5c97d6ca967.mp4?t=1698896750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
